desc_long								关于这款软件							ASMRAutonomous sensory meridian response (ASMR) is defined as pleasurable tingling sensations in the head, scalp, back, or anywhere in the body in response to visual, auditory, tactile, olfactory, or cognitive stimuli.Wikipedia page on the study of ASMR: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Autonomous_sensory_meridian_responseASMR also aids in relaxation and sleep. Many people experience ASMR differently. ASMR Universe gives the user the power to shape a complete universe of sounds.FEATURESMore than 80 sounds (more to be added on user recommendation)The ability to create sounds paths which moves the sounds across a sound space through different speakers/audio space(left, right, behind, etc)The ability to save and load universesSounds can be recorded with 'r' and will be saved as a wav file in the game's installation directoryCharacters can be selected using keys 1-6 (cat,dog,owl,penguin,rat,wolf) Relax at home, work, while you game						
